            <title>[HIVE-24803] WorkloadManager doesn&apos;t update allocation and metrics after Kill Trigger action</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-24803</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;At present after the query is killed following metrics are not updated by Workload Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;numRunningQueries&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;numExecutors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Also, The WorkloadManager doesn&apos;t add update the pool allocations after the query is killed i.e. poolsToRedistribute doesn&apos;t contain the pool name for which the query is killed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
